# strategy
## Use "incognito mode" or a VPN
Flight websites abuse tracking cookies to push prices up.

## Short-term
Many last-minute deals happen 1-2 weeks before departure, as airlines scramle
to fill seats.

## Long-term
fly off-season/shoulder season



# websites
## Google flights
https://www.google.com/flights
Really nice UI. No experience using this yet.

## Holiday Pirate
Apparently really good at last-minute flight deals. No experience using it

## Skyscanner
https://www.skyscanner.net/
Search by month(cheapest month) is a great feature.
